{"word":"λωβητός","slug":"λωβητός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λωβητός</b></el> <el>(λωβητός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:λωβάομαι'><el>λωβάομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>despitefully treated, outraged</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>insulting, abusive</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}